{"tid":218654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港民族黨地區演講】","createTime":"2017-04-26T15:58:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T07:10:18.000Z","uid":28366,"like":42,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d682f591ab452138f6dd2528d914f9d22719e9d0","tid":218654,"uid":28366,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:58:31.000Z","msg":"集會為政治活動不可缺少一環。為鞏固獨派的勢力及令支持者與港人能恆常參與政治活動，視之為日常生活的一部份，敝黨將定期於各區演講及舉辦集會，向普羅大眾解釋推動獨立的條件及必要性。演講將釋述殖民政策容許中國人在香港竊取各項資源，包括公屋、學位、綜援等福利，甚至妨礙港人向上流動，由此將港共殖民政府及主流媒體絕口不提的論述推而廣之，使大眾藉此了解香港獨立之逼切。    <br />\n<br />\n此外，獨立運動決非一時一刻之事，重整獨派旗號及擴大影響力乃首要工作。敝黨將演講、集會視為鞏固獨派勢力的渠道，令香港獨立融入港人的日常生活，從而使獨派的政治理念逐一實現。主講為敝黨召集人陳浩天及發言人周浩輝，冀獨派支持者及公眾親赴現場支持。<br />\n<br />\n首次地區演講詳情如下：<br />\n日期：4月30日（日）<br />\n時間：下午4時30分 - 5時30分 <br />\n地點：尖沙咀文化中心映月樓外<br />\n&mdash;------<br />\n▋推動香港獨立有賴各位參與，請支持民族黨營運<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hknationalparty.com/product/fin_scheme/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hknationalparty.com%2Fproduct%2Ffin_scheme%2F&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=018449ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hknationalparty.com/product/fin_scheme/</a><br />\n▋地區工作招募<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/YBRfzkiwrBRfMu6D3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FYBRfzkiwrBRfMu6D3&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=7947f703\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/YBRfzkiwrBRfMu6D3</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/26/235732_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F26%2F235732_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0ea7b8b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fae15017a037c441b2275e7cbf8fab9a36b9a1b5","tid":218654,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T16:02:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/xUA7bfZRArz3cDnKV2/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg